motoLM DB:

Tables:

Users:
User {userId, username, password}
Roles {basic, manager}
UserRoles {userId, role}

Competitions:
Riders {riderId, firstName, lastName, dateOfBirth, phoneNo}
Motorbikes{bikeId, bikeType, engine,...}
Categories {categoryId, categoryName}
Courses {courseId, courseName}
TourDetails {courseId, tourDate}
RiderMotorbike {riderID, bikeId}
RiderCategories {riderId, categoryId}
Results {riderId, bikeId, categoryId, courseId, tourDate, result, position}